{
  "stem": "93.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "There were baskets and baskets full of hair, which they had taken out that they were going to apparently use to stuff mattresses and things like that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They-- they had soap that had been made out of human oils, which the camp personnel had extracted by boiling human beings and then saponifying the oil.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And then, I remember in particular-- and I saw this later at the war crimes trial-- we had captured a-- a box that was about this big and about this wide.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And it was filled with alcohol.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And as you looked at it from one side, there was a human head in it in profile, and the neck had been cut.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here was the head.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when you turned it around like this, what you saw were all of the cavities of-- of the head.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that somebody had very carefully sawn this head in half, and then mounted it in this thing for some kind of medical experiment.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I will tell you later about some of the experiments that were conducted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, we then continued our march east.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by this time, the German army essentially was defeated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the concentration camp system was beginning to fall apart, and the inmates were beginning to crowd the roads and became refugees.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were moving in both directions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were refugees from places like Belgium, France, Luxembourg, as well as people from the-- from the Eastern nations, as well as Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were many Russian soldiers in these camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So anyway, we then began to get reports virtually every day of new camps being liberated, of new groups of people being found.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
